TI  - Assessment of terrain stability zones for human habitation in Himalayan Upper Pindar River Basin, Uttarakhand using AHP and GIS
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL EARTH SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - Terrain stability zones
