TI  - Characterization and applicability of novel alkali-tolerant carbonatogenic bacteria as environment-friendly bioconsolidants for management of concrete structures and soil erosion
T2  - JOURNAL OF ENVIRONMENTAL MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Arthrobacter sulfureus
KW  - Biorestoration
KW  - Carbonatogenesis
KW  - Calcium carbonate
KW  - Sustainability
