TI  - The Late Quaternary activity characteristics of the Lixian-Luojiabu fault: A discussion on the seismogenic mechanism of the Lixian <i>M</i>8 earthquake in 1654
T2  - CHINESE JOURNAL OF GEOPHYSICS-CHINESE EDITION
