TI  - Salicylic acid activates poplar defense against the biotrophic rust fungus <i>Melampsora larici-populina</i> via increased biosynthesis of catechin and proanthocyanidins
T2  - NEW PHYTOLOGIST
LA  - English
KW  - benzothiadiazole (BTH)
KW  - chemical defense
KW  - condensed tannins
