FX  - We thank the Museum of New Zealand Te Papa Tongarewa and DoC for funding assistance for our ongoing research programme. K.-J.W. thanks the Brian Mason Trust for the funding of her 2016 review of threats to Westland Petrels that contributed greatly to this paper. We thank the West Coast Penguin Trust for their support for Westland Petrel research and conservation efforts in the region. Thanks to Rod Hitchmough, Barry Baker, Wieslawa Misiak, and Richard Phillips for comments on the draft. Thanks to Tim Poupart, Reuben Lane, and many DOC and Te Papa staff who have assisted with the field programmes over time. An anonymous reviewer and N. Carlile offered helpful comments that improved the paper.
