TI  - Potential Applications of Open Weave Jute Geotextile (Soil Saver) in Meeting Geotechnical Difficulties
T2  - 3RD INTERNATIONAL CONFERENCE ON NATURAL FIBERS: ADVANCED MATERIALS FOR A GREENER WORLD, ICNF 2017
LA  - English
CP  - 3rd International Conference on Natural Fibers - Advanced Materials for a Greener World (ICNF)
