KW  - Bulk segregant analysis
KW  - Nematode resistance genes
KW  - PLANT-PARASITIC NEMATODES
KW  - MELOIDOGYNE-GRAMINICOLA
KW  - GENE
KW  - GENOME
KW  - SUSCEPTIBILITY
