TI  - Image Processing of UAV Imagery for River Feature Recognition of Kerian River, Malaysia
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - image processing
KW  - unmanned aerial vehicle
KW  - feature recognition
KW  - image segmentation
KW  - color space
