TI  - Field based index of flood vulnerability (IFV): A new validation technique for flood susceptible models
T2  - GEOSCIENCE FRONTIERS
LA  - English
KW  - Flood susceptibility
KW  - Flood vulnerability
KW  - Machine learning
KW  - Index of flood vulnerability
KW  - Flood simulation model
