TI  - Linking hydrological, infinite slope stability and land-use change models through GIS for assessing the impact of deforestation on slope stability in high Andean watersheds
T2  - GEOMORPHOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - land-use change
KW  - infinite slope analysis
KW  - hydrology
KW  - slope movement
