AB  - The information on mountain lakes of Central Asia with unstable dams is presented. The possible changes of their regime under influence warming of a climate caused by growth of concentration greenhouse gases are considered (examined). On an example of largest landslide and Sarez lake the necessity of the further development of works in this direction is shown.
