T2  - ROCK AND SOIL MECHANICS
LA  - Chinese
KW  - thrust at front end of slope
KW  - unsaturated residual soil slope
KW  - real-time response
KW  - residual slide force
KW  - effect of soil softening
KW  - ARTIFICIAL RAINFALL
KW  - INDUCED LANDSLIDES
KW  - STABILITY
KW  - FAILURE
KW  - TESTS
